 2Q17 Results: Telefônica Brasil S.A. 
         










    










 













 











 



















2Q17 Results: Telefônica Brasil S.A.
        																																															
              











 News provided by
Telefônica Brasil S.A.  
Jul 26, 2017, 06:03 ET









 Share this article




























































SAO PAULO, July 26, 2017 /PRNewswire/ -- Telefônica Brasil - (Bovespa: VIVT3 [Common Shares] / VIVT4 [Preferred Shares]; NYSE:   VIV), announces its results for the 2Q17. Solid performance in mobile data and ultra-broadband, and continuous efficiency in costs and investments drives to strong 6.9% y-o-y growth in recurring EBITDA and 11.7% y-o-y growth in Operating Cash Flow.












